<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF6E6AD1FD709B0A1D38B646" baseAuthorityName="Scully" baseAuthorityYear="1881" box="[652,824,3411,3444]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Murina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="149" pageNumber="910" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="tubinaris">M. tubinaris</taxonomicName>
, but split on genetic and morphological grounds. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
